### Why gRPC?

gRPC plugins are better for:
- Heavy I/O operations (direct filesystem, network access)
- Using native Go libraries
- Debugging (can attach debugger to separate process)
- Complex integrations with external services

For most plugins, WASM is recommended (portable, sandboxed).

